snippet.title: Squid Game: Unleashed | Official Announcement Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
You win some, you die some. Use skill and quick reflexes to survive twisted competitions in this multiplayer action game inspired by the hit series. Squid Game: Unleashed is coming soon to the Netflix App. Find out more at https://squidgameunleashed.com

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.
